description:
Our company’s main area is custom web development and design. We have experience in developing various projects, such as CRM systems, e-commerce, SaaS, and startups.
Our main tech skills are:
PHP, Laravel framework, Yii2 framework;
MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB;
JavaScript, React, Vue.js;
HTML, CSS, Bootstrap;
Web design, UI/UX, responsive design, wireframing, prototyping. 
Our team of professionals offers a full cycle of project development from wireframing and design to deployment and support. Quality Assurance and Project Management are included in the development process by default.
While working on a project, we try to make the process as transparent as possible. For every client and project, we:
define the scope and write a specification document and optionally create wireframes before the start - it helps both sides to be on the same page;
split a project to milestones and work by iterations;
provide reports with agreed frequency;
present work on own stage server;
have scheduled Skype calls for discussing any questions;
create a shared Trello board to keep track of tasks and statuses (or use any other Task Tracking System).
We respond within 24 hours to emails and other messages. Our Sales and Project Managers have an advanced level of spoken and written English and have significant experience in communicating with clients all around the world.
We are looking forward to working with you!
